13.post('/getGroupByUser')
	input: teacher_id /** not user_id to show that it only occures in teacher as user type **/
    output: status 200 & json with all groups and tasks /400 - server error
    example to output : 	
{  "groups": [
	{
      "GroupId": 1111,
      "GroupName": "בדיקות",
      "teacherID": "1",
      "IsMasterGroup": 1,
      "GroupeCode": "01111"
    },
    {
      "GroupId": 1234567,
      "GroupName": "שיעור פרטי",
      "teacherID": "1",
      "IsMasterGroup": 0,
      "GroupeCode": "0123456"
    }
  ],
  "tasks": [
    {
      "T_id": 1,
      "T_title": "מטלת ניסוי",
      "T_description": "מטלת ניסוי לבסיס הנתונים"
    },
